      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not alone in feeling this way, and the loss of your \"self\" is a serious struggle that deserves deep understanding, not judgment. Many people experience moments where they feel like a facade, but reaching out to a professional can offer a safe space to explore these feelings without the pressure of performing for others. Sometimes, simply speaking with someone who listens without trying to fix you can help you reconnect with whatever genuine parts remain inside.",
